import React, { useState } from "react"; import { Modal } from "react-bootstrap"; import SelectYears from "../inputs/select-years"; import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"; import "../css/registration-modal.css"; import { useForm } from "react-hook-form"; import * as yup from "yup"; import { yupResolver } from "@hookform/resolvers/yup"; const RegistrationModal = ({ ...props }) => { const schema = yup.object().shape({ firstName: yup .string() .firstName() .required() .pattern(/^[A-Za-z]+$/i), email: yup.string().email().required(), password: yup.string().min(8).max(32).required(), }); const { register, handleSubmit, formState: { errors }, reset, } = useForm({ resolver: yupResolver(schema), }); const onSubmitHandler = (data) => { console.log({ data }); reset(); }; return (
Sign Up
It's quick and easy.

{errors.firstName?.message}

{errors.lastName?.type === "required" && "Last name is required"}

By clicking Sign Up, you agree to our Terms,{" "} Data Policy and Cookie Policy. You may receive SMS notifications from us and can opt out at any time.
); }; export default RegistrationModal;
